metadata.description: DRP.io, the world's first blue chip NFT platform, presents lushsux.io - the Instagram collection. With over 20 years in the game, the "world's first and therefore best" meme artist LushSux has built a portfolio of 4444 posts, 900K followers and 1.3B likes. Now you can own part of this history.
